<h2 class="govuk-heading-m">What happens next</h2>
<p class="govuk-body">We’ll let <%= @lead_provider&.name %> and <%= @delivery_partner&.name %> know that your school wants
  to make a change for ECTs and
  mentors starting in the 2022 to 2023 academic year.</p>
<p class="govuk-body">They may contact you to confirm this.</p>

<h2 class="govuk-heading-m">What to do next</h2>
<p>As soon as possible:</p>
<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet govuk-list--spaced">
  <li>confirm the change with your new lead provider</li>
  <% if !appropriate_body_appointed? %>
    <li>tell us which appropriate body you’ve appointed for your ECTs</li>
  <% end %>
  <li>add the new ECTs and mentors to this service so we can check their eligibility for DfE funding</li>
  <li>use this service to tell us which mentor has been assigned to each ECT</li>
</ul>

<p>
  <a href="<%= step_by_step_path %>" rel="noreferrer noopener" target="_blank">
    Read our step by step guidance (opens in new tab)
  </a>
  if you need more help.
</p>
